</p>
<p>The overcloud options define the configurations of the overcloud. You can define the configurations for <xref href="../../commercial/GA1/1.1commercial.undercloud-oc-config-esx.xml" >ESX Clusters</xref>, <xref href="../../commercial/GA1/1.1commercial.undercloud-oc-config-storevirtual.xml" >StoreVirtual Backends</xref>, and <xref href="../../commercial/GA1/1.1commercial.undercloud-oc-config-storeserv.xml" >StoreServ Backends</xref>.</p>
<p>To define the configuration:</p>
<ol>
<li>Log in to the undercloud Horizon Dashboard.</li>
<li>In the left panel, click the <b>Overcloud</b> tab.</li>
<li>Click <b>Configure</b>.</li>
<li>Select the desired tab on the Configure Cloud page:<b>ESX Clusters</b>, <b>StoreVirtual Backends</b> and <b>StoreServ Backends</b>.</li>
</ol>
